source.name: NSF Freedom of Information Act Report for October 1, 2006 through September 30, 2007
source.description: This file contains the National Science Foundation's 2007 FOIA Annual Report. The report provides detailed information regarding the number and type of FOIA cases we processed in FY 2007. It also includes data regarding time and costs associated with processing these cases.
